data.description: Welcome to your dream home in North Forsyth: a stunning bi-level retreat nestled on more than 6 acres! Step onto the large covered front porch - perfect for rocking chairs and sweet tea sipping - and walk inside to a bright and airy interior bathed in natural light. The open-concept layout seamlessly integrates with the gorgeous hardwood floors that span the entire home. Updates are evident at every turn, ensuring modern comfort and style.     The heart of this home is its completely renovated kitchen, featuring top-of-the-line appliances, a stylish backsplash, beautifully refinished cabinets, and birch butcher block countertops. No detail has been spared, including the charming farmhouse sink that overlooks a picturesque window view.     The attention to detail extends to the updated primary and hall bath, laundry room, and basement, where you'll discover an impressive second kitchen/canning room, flex room, bathroom, workshop, and boat door.     The fully fenced and cross-fenced 6+ acres feature two beehives and orchards with apple, plum, cherry, peach, pear, and almond trees, along with elderberry and blackberry bushes. Also enjoy fresh blueberries from your own bushes, complemented by grapevines and a spring-fed creek. The 3-stall barn currently houses goats and chickens, but is also the perfect home for horses. The flat backyard offers the perfect foundation for an in-ground pool.     This home not only offers a peaceful retreat, but it is in Forsyth County’s top-notch school district and convenient to GA-400 and the North Georgia Outlet malls. Don't miss the opportunity to make this slice of paradise your own!
